# React Standards

## State Management
- **Local:** `useState`, `useReducer`
- **UI/App:** Context, Zustand, Redux Toolkit
- **Server:** React Query (preferred) or SWR
- **Form:** React-Hook-Form

## File Organization
- **Co-location:** `Button.tsx`, `Button.test.tsx`, `Button.stories.tsx` together
- **Named exports:** Preferred over default exports
- **Barrel exports:** `index.ts` in each folder

